{
  "stem": "24195.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were all insulting me and called, called it-- that this is-- what are you doing?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're riding Abraham's sled, you know, in, in, [SPEAKING GERMAN], you know, in, in German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I-- that was not very complimentary and very nice of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I had to live with these kind of things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, these things would never stop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it probably was for the best.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That I left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was for the best that I probably left school because the humiliation and embarrassment would have only grown more stronger, you know, after that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I remember the, the Hitler Youth movement and the victories that the German Army had during the early years of the war really contributed to this atmosphere of self-assurance and of overwhelming victorious feelings, you know.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember when I was in high school-- until I got kicked out-- that the-- you know, they-- even over the intercom system on the-- in schools, they would put on the special announcement that there was another big victory in the North Atlantic that had sank so many more American or British fighters, you know.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so then there-- it was almost like a short celebration every time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people would take a break from your program.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they would all go-- and I remember in the class where I was in, they would all run to the-- to the map-- where the big map was and pinpointing the situation where the, the, the attack was by the German submarines.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they would all say, oh, well it's only a matter of time when Germany wins the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- a very interesting memory, there was one young blonde kid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He looked very German, was young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "His name was-- his last name was Krafft.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
